data.description: Gorgeous light and bright immaculate 3 bedroom 2 bath home with an office/den and an extended 2 car garage in a lovely gated community. High ceilings, wonderful split floor plan, New Roof in August of 2023. Zoned for Shady Hill Elementary School. Beautifully landscaped privacy fenced backyard. Spacious great room with triple sliders leading to a 9' x 17' screened Lanai that extends out to a 14' x 24' screened atrium enclosure, providing extra entertaining space, and the hot tub will stay with the home. Beautiful high-end maple wood cabinets in kitchen, large pantry, eat-at bar plus a dining area. The appliances and HVAC come with a transferrable warranty. Separate formal dining room. Large walk-in closet in master bedroom. Garden tub, separate shower and double vanities in master bath. Both bathrooms have a linen closet. Inside laundry room with laundry sink. Garage ceiling has R 30 insulation and the garage door is also insulated. The fence is constructed of treated wood. TV jacks in every room, including the lanai. Convenient location: Just 8 minutes to Publix, 10 minutes To downtown Ocala. Approximately 15 minutes to the Paddock Mall, lots of shopping and restaurants, Silver Springs State Park, the World Equestrian Center, multiple golf courses and I-75. Very easy commute to Gainesville too. Great home!
